-- Standard Chartered Appoints Tom Welch as Global Head of Cash Equity Sales
-- Shiyin Chen
-- 2010-07-08T01:33:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/standard-chartered-appoints-tom-welch-as-global-head-of-cash-equity-sales.html

          
          
             Standard Chartered Plc said it
appointed Tom Welch as global head of cash equities sales.  
 Welch, who was most recently head of research sales for
Asia excluding Japan at Deutsche Bank AG, starts today and is
based in Hong Kong, Standard Chartered Bank said in an e-mailed
statement.  
